summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to vehicles and traffic; amending Sections 11.26.020, 11.26.060, 11.26.080, 11.26.100, 11.26.120, 11.26.160, 11.26.180, 11.26.240, 11.26.260, 11.26.280 and 11.26.290 of the Seattle Municipal Code, to provide fees for the service of hooding parking meters; and to define and identify the two types of service parking permits (building or on-street).
